      "instruction": "<p>Slice <strong>half</strong> your <strong>chilli[es]</strong> finely into rounds (you'll use the rest later!)</p><p>Zest your <strong>lime[s]</strong></p><p>Peel your <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Combine 1 tsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tsp]</span> <strong>sugar </strong>in a bowl with the juice of <strong>half</strong> the <strong>lime[s] </strong>and the <strong>chilli rounds</strong> and set aside – this is your <strong>quick-pickled chilli</strong></p>",
