      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>coconut marinated chicken</strong> and cook for 6 min on each side or until slightly charred and cooked through (no pink meat!) – this is your <strong>spicy coconut chicken</strong></p><p>Tip: Cooking for 5? You may need to do this in batches!</p>",
